flowchart TB
    USER[Human Operator / SRE] --> UI[Next.js OpsPilot Dashboard<br/>Vercel Frontend]

    UI --> API[FastAPI Backend API<br/>Incident + Approval Endpoints]

    API --> ORCH[Multi-Agent Incident Orchestrator<br/>Coordinates agents and stores timeline]

    ORCH --> INVESTIGATION[Investigation Agents<br/>Triage + Observability + Runbook Retrieval]
    ORCH --> REASONING[Reasoning Agents<br/>Hypothesis + Remediation Planning]
    ORCH --> SAFETY[Safety Agents<br/>Risk Review + Human Approval Brief]
    ORCH --> EXECUTION[Execution Agents<br/>Remediation + Review + Postmortem]

    INVESTIGATION --> TOOLS[Operational Tools<br/>Metrics + Logs + Deployment History + Runbooks]
    REASONING --> QWEN[Qwen Cloud Model API<br/>Real mode after credits]
    SAFETY --> QWEN
    EXECUTION --> QWEN

    SAFETY --> APPROVAL{Human Approval Required?}

    APPROVAL -->|Approved| ACTION[Controlled Remediation Simulation]
    APPROVAL -->|Blocked| ESCALATE[Stop / Escalate]

    ACTION --> VERIFY[Before / After Verification]
    VERIFY --> POSTMORTEM[Generated Postmortem]

    ORCH --> AUDIT[Agent Timeline<br/>Audit Trail]
    ORCH --> STATE[Incident State Store]

    API -. planned backend deployment .-> ECS[Alibaba Cloud ECS<br/>Dockerized FastAPI Backend]
